HEADWORD: Juglans
<hw>Jug"lans</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.,
walnut.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of valuable trees,
including the true walnut of Europe, and the America black walnut, and
butternut.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

